# alexa-downchannel (Node.js)

- Uses `http`/`https` stdlib only — no external deps
- Cookie from env `COOKIE_SERVER_URL`; refresh at startup
- GraphQL at `https://alexa.amazon.com/nexus/v1/graphql`; headers: Cookie, csrf, Accept, Content-Type, User-Agent, Referer, Origin
- Endpoints: `/ping`, `/health`, `/refresh`, `/poll`
- Push to Hubitat: POST `{HUBITAT_URL}/apps/api/{APP_ID}/statusreportfromtheapp?access_token=...`
